Output examples/sample-hiring-tool/terminal-scan.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1160
Set Height 560
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20
Set Margin 30
Set MarginFill "#1e1e2e"
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set BorderRadius 10
Set TypingSpeed 55ms

Hide
Type "cd /Users/fardakarimov/Desktop/Playground/compliance-agent && clear"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

Type "compliance-agent scan examples/sample-hiring-tool --quiet"
Sleep 700ms
Enter
Sleep 5s
Screenshot examples/sample-hiring-tool/terminal-scan-final.png
Sleep 3s
